Source: max-meta
Section: max
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Pedro Peña Pérez <pedro.pena@edmanufacturer.es>
Standards-Version: 3.7.2
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4), cdbs

Package: max-desktop
Architecture: all
Depends: max-desktop-common, max-desktop-gnome | max-desktop-kde | max-desktop-xfce
Description: The Max desktop system
 This package depends on all of the packages in the Max desktop system
 .
 It is also used to help ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that
 it not be removed.

Package: max-desktop-gnome
Architecture: all
Depends: max-desktop-common, ${max-desktop-gnome:Depends}
Recommends: ${max-desktop-gnome:Recommends}
Provides: max-desktop
Description: The Max desktop system (GNOME desktop)
 This package depends on all GNOME packages in the Max desktop system
 .
 It is also used to help ensure proper upgrades, so it is recommended that
 it not be removed.

